Hey, Jason.

01:00.843 --> 01:01.887
Hey.

01:03.063 --> 01:04.325
Hi. Do you know what you want?

01:04.499 --> 01:05.413
- Uh, yeah.
- Cool.

01:05.587 --> 01:06.805
