the final girl,

03:07.056 --> 03:08.013
the different rules:

03:08.188 --> 03:10.973
Don't split up. Don't have sex.

03:12.975 --> 03:15.238
<i>Don't answer the phone.</i> Exactly, exactly, exactly.

03:15.412 --> 03:16.761
