comes an opportunity

03:18.807 --> 03:20.330
for outsider art.

03:20.504 --> 03:22.724
A voice for the voiceless,
you might say.

03:22.898 --> 03:24.552
<i>Mmm.</i>
Jesus Christ.

03:24.726 --> 03:26.771
<i>Yeah, I'm more of
a rom-com guy,
to be honest.</i>

03:26.945 --> 03:29.470
<i>Okay, I think I'm on Hudson.</i>

03:29.644 --> 03:31.080
