04:15.820 --> 04:18.562
<i>Wait. Really? Are you sure?</i>

04:18.736 --> 04:20.129
Uh...

04:22.305 --> 04:23.654
Let me just...

04:23.828 --> 04:27.310
<i>Uh, there are some dumpsters
about halfway down.</i>

04:28.180 --> 04:30.705
