04:58.385 --> 04:59.690
<i>Okay, this is weird.</i>

05:01.126 --> 05:04.304
<i>Um...
Now they're moving towards me.</i>

05:04.478 --> 05:05.348
Are you okay?

05:05.522 --> 05:07.350
<i>Shit. He's following me.</i>

05:07.524 --> 05:09.178
