05:09.352 --> 05:12.137
<i>Holy shit! He's after me!</i>

05:12.312 --> 05:13.356
Where are you?

05:13.530 --> 05:15.576
<i>He's got a knife!</i> What?

05:15.750 --> 05:18.187
