10:49.736 --> 10:53.565
<i>I just want you to tell me
why you think
you're doing this.</i>

10:53.740 --> 10:54.741
<i>In your words.</i>

10:54.915 --> 10:56.351
We're finishing
Richie's film.

10:56.525 --> 10:58.832
<i>That's right,
by killing Sam and Tara.</i>

10:59.006 --> 11:00.355
Why are you fucking with me?

11:01.225 --> 11:03.053
