11:06.317 --> 11:08.058
<i>I'm here.</i>

11:10.495 --> 11:13.411
<i>Let's play a game.</i>[sighs] Shit.

11:13.585 --> 11:15.283
<i>Do you know Warmer, Colder?</i>

11:15.457 --> 11:17.502
<i>Come on, find me.</i>

11:17.677 --> 11:19.896
<i>And then we'll go and cut up
the Carpenter sisters.</i>

11:20.070 --> 11:22.116
Are you using
the fucking cameras?

11:22.290 --> 11:23.900
<i>Yeah. The cameras.</i>

11:24.074 --> 11:27.948
<i>And at the moment,
you're very, very cold.</i>

11:28.122 --> 11:29.906
All right, douchebag,
let's play.

11:37.784 --> 11:39.350
<i>Cold.</i>

11:45.008 --> 11:46.662
<i>Heating up.</i>

11:52.276 --> 11:53.408
<i>Warmer.</i>

11:56.411 --> 11:57.542
<i>Warmer.</i>

12:13.950 --> 12:15.822
All right, you know what?
This is stupid.

12:15.996 --> 12:17.171
