12:17.345 --> 12:18.868
<i>But you're getting warmer.</i>

12:23.830 --> 12:25.092
<i>Colder.</i>

12:32.447 --> 12:33.535
<i>Warmer.</i>

12:35.450 --> 12:36.581
<i>Warmer.</i>

